<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2007-01-01</DATELINE><TITLE>Ten years of fighting bird flu</TITLE><BODY>This year marks a decade since the first human outbreak of H5N1 avian influenza in Hong Kong. Since then, US $1.9 billion has been pledged to fight avian influenza and a global effort is under way to prevent and be prepared for a pandemic.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>